include ../../atoms/checkbox/checkbox.pug
mixin EmptyCartAccordionGroup()
  .accordion.group.js-accordion
    +AccordionItem("How do I buy an NFT?", 0)
      p Browse the marketplace, pick an NFT you like, and click <strong>Buy Now</strong>. Before purchasing, connect your MetaMask wallet using the <strong>Connect a wallet</strong> link in the footer. Payments run on the Sepolia test network, so no real money is spent.
    +AccordionItem("What happens after I pay?", 1)
      p MetaMask asks you to confirm the transaction. Once it is approved on Sepolia, the NFT is added to your cart and a receipt is saved. You can review purchased items anytime on the Cart page.
    +AccordionItem("Why do I need a crypto wallet?", 2)
      p NFT marketplaces use wallets to identify buyers and process payments securely. MetaMask acts as your digital wallet. For this demo we use Sepolia test ETH — you can get free test coins from a Sepolia faucet and practice without risk.
